play-interview", "id": 1516867, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/478584/dimension-20-never-stop-blowing-up-rules-system-official", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Finally, Dimension 20 fans can Never Stop Blowing Up at their own home tables", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T13:41:31+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/The-Magnus-Archives-RPG-127-Gabriela-Novotna.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The highly-anticipated <a href=\"https://www.montecookgames.com/store/product/the-magnus-archives-roleplaying-game/\"><em>Magnus Archives</em> <em>Roleplaying Game</em></a> is finally available for purchase. Based on <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/podcasts/2020/5/19/21263119/7-popular-podcasts-with-lots-of-episodes\">the cult-classic podcast</a>, the tabletop RPG hit (virtual) shelves earlier this month after raising over $2 million dollars during its crowdfunding campaign in late 2023. Anyone can purchase the physical edition through <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/2022/8/3/23289239/monte-cook-games-numenera-decade-anniversary-the-weir", "id": 1516868, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/478911/magnus-archives-rpg-monte-cook-games-where-to-buy", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The Magnus Archives RPG based on the cult-classic podcast goes on sale\u00a0", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T13:18:11+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Epic Games via MobyGames\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/unreal.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Unreal</em>, the first-person shooter that introduced Unreal Engine to the world, and its multiplayer-focused follow-up <em>Unreal Tournament</em> have been preserved via the Internet Archive and are <a href=\"https://www.resetera.com/threads/epic-games-gives-the-thumbs-up-to-archive-org-copies-of-unreal-gold-and-unreal-tournament-goty-free-to-download-for-all.1035414\">freely available for download</a> with the blessing of developer Epic Games.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><a href=\"https://www.oldunreal.com\">Old Unreal</a> first shared the news with its longstanding community of diehard <em>Unreal</em> fans <a href=\"https://discord.c", "id": 1516869, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/479060/unreal-tournament-epic-games-internet-archive-free", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Unreal, Unreal Tournament free on Internet Archive", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T10:50:37+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Fortnite Chapter 2 Remix Ice Isle\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Epic Games\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-ice-isle-ice-sp_bced3a.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>Fortnite Remix</strong> is the revival and remix of Chapter 2 maps that are part of the shortened season and <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/fortnite-guide/473857/remix-season-schedule-dates-when-does-it-end\">weekly refresh schedule</a>.</p>\n\n<p>The month-long season started with a live event and kicked off the Remix season with The Doggfather, Snoop Dogg, and continued with the addition of one Slim Shady, Eminem. This season\u2019s weekly updates will a tour through Chapter 2 with updates each Thursday unvaulting weapons and vehicles that are new, old, or remixed.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Let\u2019s t", "id": 1515432, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/fortnite-guide/478987/remix-week-3-loot-pool-map-changes", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "What are the new map and weapon loot pool changes in Fortnite Remix\u2019s Week 3 update?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T10:29:31+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Fortnite Remix Ice Spice\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Epic Games via Polygon\ufeff\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/fortnite-chapter-2-remix-ice-spice-1920x.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><strong>Ice Spice </strong>and <strong>Ice Isle </strong>are the Week 3 additions to Nov. 2024\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/fortnite-guide/475617/remix-season-schedule-dates-when-does-it-end\">Fortnite Remix</a>.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The remixed version of Chapter 2 is highlighting a different musician each week, with a remixed Shark becoming Ice Isle and home to Ice Spice herself.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Here\u2019s where you can find Ice Spice and her POI (point of interest) Ice Isle in <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/fortnite-battle-royale/40155\">F", "id": 1515433, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/fortnite-guide/478962/ice-spice-isle-location-remix-where-to-find", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Where is Ice Spice and Ice Isle in Fortnite Remix?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T10:10:03+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Cameron Faulkner/Polygon | Source images: Herman Miller, Logitech, Secretlab, Noblechairs\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24944272/bestgamingchairs.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"is-lead\">The <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/what-to-buy/23885770/best-gaming-chairs\">best gaming chairs</a> provide comfort, style, and features that normal office chairs can\u2019t match. Sure, getting one might run you a few hundred dollars more than perhaps you were expecting to pay, but the same rationale for splashing cash on a good bed works here, too. That is to say, if you\u2019re sitting at your desk for eight hours or more per day, investing in a comfortable chair that\u2019s going to make you happy for several years is a sound idea.\u00a0</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-a", "id": 1515434, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/what-to-buy/23885770/best-gaming-chairs", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The best gaming chairs", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-14T09:36:59+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Nintendo EPD/Nintendo via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24648384/Tears_of_the_Kingdom_Shrine_map_header.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Looking for the best games on the Nintendo Switch? What follows is a living list of the 25 Switch games we recommend everyone play or watch \u2014 in case you\u2019re new to the system or you\u2019re just looking for something new to play.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The Switch has been around over seven years, has sold more than 140 million units, and boasts a vast software library encompassing first-party Nintendo classics, major games from big publishers, and a bewildering array 